OL,3,CU-turn gives football club chance to
OL,4,Cplay promotion decider at home
OL,6,FGuernsey FC's play-off final against
OL,7,FPeacehaven & Telscombe will take place
OL,8,Fat Victoria Park on 23 May.
OL,10,FIt comes after league officials
OL,11,Fdecided initially decided to switch
OL,12,Fthe match's venue to one in the UK.
OL,14,FHowever, following discussions with
OL,15,Ftheir opponents and the Southern
OL,16,FCombination Football League Board, the
OL,17,Fgame will be played in Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
