OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778512268
OL,3,CU-turn gives football club chance to
OL,4,Cplay promotion decider at home
OL,6,FIn a statement, Nic Legg, Guernsey
OL,7,FFC's director, said: "From the
OL,8,Funforgettable scenes of jubilation
OL,9,Flast Saturday to the frustration,
OL,10,Fdisappointment and disbelief that
OL,11,Ffollowed, it has been an emotional
OL,12,Frollercoaster for everyone connected
OL,13,Fwith Guernsey FC.
OL,15,F"But now our focus turns firmly
OL,16,Ftowards what lies ahead.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
