OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778512268
OL,3,CU-turn gives football club chance to
OL,4,Cplay promotion decider at home
OL,6,F"The countdown has begun to Guernsey
OL,7,FFC's first ever play-off final, and
OL,8,Fwhat an occasion it promises to be. A
OL,9,Fplay-off final at Victoria Park in
OL,10,Ffront of our island community is
OL,11,Fexactly what we set out to achieve
OL,12,Fwhen this season began.
OL,14,F"The players have earned this
OL,15,Fopportunity. Our supporters deserve
OL,16,Fthis moment. Now it is time for the
OL,17,Fwhole island to come together once
OL,18,Fagain and turn Victoria Park into the
OL,19,Ffortress we all know it can be.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778512268
OL,3,CU-turn gives football club chance to
OL,4,Cplay promotion decider at home
OL,6,F"There is something incredibly special
OL,7,Fabout the prospect of competing for
OL,8,Fpromotion on home soil. These are the
OL,9,Foccasions football is all about. The
OL,10,Fatmosphere, the emotion, the sense of
OL,11,Fcommunity and togetherness. It has all
OL,12,Fthe ingredients to become one of the
OL,13,Fmost memorable afternoons in Guernsey
OL,14,FFC's history.
OL,16,F"We want every single person connected
OL,17,Fwith the club and Guernsey football to
OL,18,Fbe part of it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
